<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Malgun Gothic', sans-serif;
      font-size: 12px;
      padding: 30px;
    }
    .title {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .info-table, .detail-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    th, td {
      border: 1px solid black;
      padding: 5px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .info-table td {
      text-align: left;
      padding-left: 10px;
    }
    .gray {
      color: gray ;
      font-size: 10px;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;

       -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
       print-color-adjust: exact;
    }
    .memo {
      padding: 10px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-top: 30px;

      -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
       print-color-adjust: exact;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .footer .line {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .footer .line input {
      width: 40px;
      border: none;
      border-bottom: 1px solid black;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer .company {
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  .detail-table thead th {
    background-color: #ccc;
    -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
       print-color-adjust: exact;
  }
  .backGray{
    background-color: #ccc;
    -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
       print-color-adjust: exact;
  }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="title">발 주 서</div>

  <table class="info-table">
    <tr>
      <td class="backGray"><strong>발주번호</strong></td>
      <td><%= mat_order_code %></td>
      <td class="backGray"><strong>발주명</strong></td>
      <td><%= mat_order_name %></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td class="backGray"><strong>거래처</strong></td>
      <td><%= company_name %></td>
      <td class="backGray"><strong>납기일자</strong></td>
      <td><%= delivery_date %></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td class="backGray"><strong>요청일자</strong></td>
      <td colspan="3"><%= request_date %></td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <p>아래와 같이 발주합니다.</p>

  <table class="detail-table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>NO</th>
        <th>자재명</th>
        <th>요청 수량</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <% detail.forEach((item, idx) => { %>
        <tr>
          <td><%= idx + 1 %></td>
          <td><%= item.mat_name %></td>
          <td><%= item.request_quantity %>개</td>
        </tr>
      <% }) %>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <div class="memo">
   비고 :  <%= note %>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    위와 같이 ☐ 발주, ☐ 견적을 요청드립니다.
    <div class="line">
      <input type="text" placeholder="202"> 년
      <input type="text" placeholder="  "> 월
      <input type="text" placeholder="  "> 일
    </div>
    <div class="company">(주)BrickFlow  拜上</div>
  </div>

  <div class="gray">※ 본 문서는 시스템에서 자동 생성된 발주서입니다.</div>

</body>
</html>
